,"msg":"<blockquote>用euler's theorem?</blockquote><br />\n越搞越似out-syl,個course冇教依樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f46154dd3c743e19d9d5a5223cfb67d733f9a3","tid":249622,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"其實係咪咁︰<br />\n<br />\n36^700 = ((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(36^7)</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><br />\n<br />\n((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: gold;\">413</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^700 mod 3233 = 413"},{"pid":"c6524b3b10e4941d4436e762d11dacf1a228ac5f","tid":249622,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪咁︰<br />\n<br />\n36^700 = ((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(36^7)</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><br />\n<br />\n((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: gold;\">413</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^700 mod 3233 = 413</blockquote><br />\n正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多字唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f97175ede274574fc9968cb81e55ca78b4911ff","tid":249622,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪咁︰<br />\n<br />\n36^700 = ((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(36^7)</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><br />\n<br />\n((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: gold;\">413</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^700 mod 3233 = 413</blockquote><br />\n正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多字唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係我都可以話2753 = 2700 + 53<br />\n36^2753<br />\n= 36^2700 * 36^53<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">36^27^10^10</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53</span><br />\n(假定一般計數機，最大食得住10^99，我咁拆陣間唔會爆10^99)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">36^27 mod 3233 = 1308<br />\n1308^10 mod 3233 = 1282<br />\n1282^10 mod 3233 = 916</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53 mod 3233 = 2262</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^2753 mod 3233<br />\n= (<span style=\"color: red;\">36^27^10^10</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53</span>) mod 3233<br />\n= (<span style=\"color: red;\">916</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">2262</span>) mod 3233<br />\n= 2872<br />\n<br />\n咁其實條題目無咩特別，<br />\n只要我部計數機食得住果個好大既數唔爆Error就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我用緊電腦個小算盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"968eb0bb0c105549f7a4a1287527efcd61dfa199","tid":249622,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪咁︰<br />\n<br />\n36^700 = ((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(36^7)</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">842</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><br />\n<br />\n((<span style=\"color: red;\">36^7</span>)<span style=\"color: orange;\">^10</span>)<span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span><br />\n= <span style=\"color: orange;\">596</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">^10</span> mod 3233<br />\n= <span style=\"color: gold;\">413</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^700 mod 3233 = 413</blockquote><br />\n正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多字唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係我都可以話2753 = 2700 + 53<br />\n36^2753<br />\n= 36^2700 * 36^53<br />\n= <span style=\"color: red;\">36^27^10^10</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53</span><br />\n(假定一般計數機，最大食得住10^99，我咁拆陣間唔會爆10^99)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">36^27 mod 3233 = 1308<br />\n1308^10 mod 3233 = 1282<br />\n1282^10 mod 3233 = 916</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53 mod 3233 = 2262</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n36^2753 mod 3233<br />\n= (<span style=\"color: red;\">36^27^10^10</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">36^53</span>) mod 3233<br />\n= (<span style=\"color: red;\">916</span> * <span style=\"color: orange;\">2262</span>) mod 3233<br />\n= 2872<br />\n<br />\n咁其實條題目無咩特別，<br />\n只要我部計數機食得住果個好大既數唔爆Error就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我用緊電腦個小算盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n用計數機就咁搵36^7  mod 3233會出843,可能有overflow問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家我索性入program入機算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}